+ * @bfq_back_penalty: weight of backward seeks wrt forward ones.
+ * @bfq_back_max: maximum allowed backward seek.
+ * @bfq_slice_idle: maximum idling time.
+ * @bfq_user_max_budget: user-configured max budget value
